{{Wireless embedded system |brand=TP-LINK |model=TD-W8951ND |revision=v4 |series=TD-W8951ND |asin=B005587N48 |fcc_date=03/07/2012 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=Yes |type=wireless router,dsl modem |fcc_id=TE7TDW8951NDV4 |ic_id=8853A-W8951NDV4 |pwr_v=9 |pwr_amp=0.85 |pwr_conn=barrel |cpu1_brand=TrendChip |cpu1_model=TC3162U |fla1=2 |fla1_brand=Eon |ram1=8 |ram1_brand=ESMT |ram1_model=M12L64164 |wi1_chip1_brand=Ralink |wi1_chip1_model=RT3390L |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_ant_conn=RP-SMA |wi1_txchains=1 |wi1_rxchains=1 |wi1_sstreams=1 |eth_cpu=true |sw_brand=TrendChip |sw_model=TC2205F |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=4 |addl_chips=DSL (ADSL2+) AFE;TrendChip;TC3086;;1; |flags=ADSL2+ |802dot11_protocols=bgn |default_ip=192.168.1.1 |default_user=admin |default_pass=admin }} {{TagLine|150Mbps Wireless N ADSL2+ Modem Router}} :[http://www.tp-link.com/en/products/details/?model=TD-W8951ND Product page]

This device uses a single-stream capable [[Ralink]] chip and a [[TrendChip]] TC3062 ADSL2+ analog front-end.
